about a week or so.

264
00:13:23,660 --> 00:13:24,825
Great. We'll let you know then.

265
00:13:24,827 --> 00:13:26,193
- Thank you very much.
- You bet.

266
00:13:26,195 --> 00:13:27,194
Great.

267
00:13:27,196 --> 00:13:28,529
[TELEPHONE RINGS]

268
00:13:28,531 --> 00:13:30,598
